{"tid":1119873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企要自己同兄弟姊妹一齊夾份買樓","createTime":"2019-04-22T08:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T18:01:32.000Z","uid":90372,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"815dd917b13713d185ebf21e978003ffb780bb43","tid":1119873,"uid":90372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"係咁既 我屋企人最近想買樓<br />\n佢地就諗住出咗首期，之後等我畢業同佢地一齊供，細妹大個就加入<br />\n層樓就落我同細妹個名<br />\n我而家就黎大學畢業，但細妹仲係幼稚園學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地就諗住將來全家人一齊住<br />\n但我係到諗我連自己將來做咩都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且要我一齊供就話我起碼都要供萬幾蚊個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係基本上佢地完全冇預我啲日常開支要錢<br />\n所以好想拒絕，但屋企人講到明一係就一齊供，一係就自己搬出去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該點做好"},{"pid":"1510dcbcb2b83d903d55ba7e29ddf26e3bf8dc3d","tid":1119873,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"搬出去住"},{"pid":"f5a2857e6481f529adffd121c94c74ddb716765a","tid":1119873,"uid":50779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b56d47f8c7cc5607370a852b70dd9f6c0f8fa11","tid":1119873,"uid":90372,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1510dcbcb2b83d903d55ba7e29ddf26e3bf8dc3d","tid":1119873,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"搬出去住"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:57:23.000Z","msg":"但搬出去住啲劏房都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擔心自己承受唔起"},{"pid":"9011b542dd9cd8b115c6bf93b0178aa6fe198629","tid":1119873,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b56d47f8c7cc5607370a852b70dd9f6c0f8fa11","tid":1119873,"uid":90372,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1510dcbcb2b83d903d55ba7e29ddf26e3bf8dc3d","tid":1119873,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s